{"tid":2309760,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【求大師解答】咩中文黎架？","createTime":"2020-12-02T18:56:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T19:12:19.000Z","uid":137277,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c59c65a91729371c0fd301991cf46eadf7d3bb05","tid":2309760,"uid":137277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T18:56:30.000Z","msg":"話說喺立場見到有篇文，有無人睇得明呢段野。。。<br />\n<br />\n雲淡輕吹，晴空廣闊，笛響起航，浪花湧濺，啞鈴外型，漁船避風，北眺亭望，樓房密集，張保仔洞，尋寶探秘，風帆花園，印記歷史，橫街窄巷，單車穿梭，坊里碰面，駐足傾談，黃昏夕照，漫步東灣，縷縷幽香，帶路指引，灰牆拉閘，樹幹檯櫈，音樂悠揚，步伐放緩，一杯咖啡，暫忘煩憂。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/personal/小島咖啡-聚友歡樂/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpersonal%2F%E5%B0%8F%E5%B3%B6%E5%92%96%E5%95%A1-%E8%81%9A%E5%8F%8B%E6%AD%A1%E6%A8%82%2F&d=u42ujRIT%2FE%2FeodHrCKN%2BOSaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=41c954f5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpersonal%2F%E5%B0%8F%E5%B3%B6%E5%92%96%E5%95%A1-%E8%81%9A%E5%8F%8B%E6%AD%A1%E6%A8%82%2F&h=8f321493\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/personal/小島咖啡-聚友歡樂/</a><br />\n究竟咩係啞鈴外型？有無人話到俾我知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea4a7f65f03574071c9694a80636b5db07d41e07","tid":2309760,"uid":137277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T18:56:46.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"51475571c82f1c18eff08f2dc58a5d3e7f71ec3a","tid":2309760,"uid":137277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T18:56:57.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"945d76896f2a1c1055ea373e1610a3982b46e706","tid":2309760,"uid":137277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T18:57:08.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"34d04f1dd97ef6039372748db2d43e15b69c38a9","tid":2309760,"uid":137277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T18:57:34.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"50f31eb48b4e8cbfc1491cd959e1485ea389286d","tid":2309760,"uid":137277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy